        <title>$^{229}$Th Nuclear Spectroscopy in an Opaque Material: Laser-Based Conversion Electron MÃ¶ssbauer Spectroscopy of $^{229}$ThO$_2$</title>
            <categories>physics.atom-ph nucl-ex physics.optics quant-ph</categories>
